.TH NEWALIASES 1 
.UC 4
.SH NAME
newaliases \- rebuild the data base for the mail aliases file
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B newaliases
.SH DESCRIPTION
.I Newaliases
rebuilds the random access data base for the mail aliases file
.IR /usr/lib/aliases .
It must be run each time
.I /usr/lib/aliases
is changed in order
for the change to take effect.
.SH SEE ALSO
aliases(4), sendmail(1M)
